            "id": 6011412,
            "title": "〈貴金屬盤後〉美就業數據強 沖淡Fed盡早降息希望 金價下挫逾1%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>周五 (6 日) 下挫逾 1%，主因是美國優於預期的非農就業報告，打擊了聯準會 (Fed) 今年立即降息的希望，不過，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>價格仍漲到 2012 年以來最高。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011412%2Fl%2F207b7f0852aabd8192983a06f1fe6e3d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈貴金屬盤後〉美就業數據強 沖淡Fed盡早降息希望 金價下挫逾1%  (圖:Shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul>\n<li>紐約<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/futures/GF/GCCON\">黃金期貨</a>下跌 0.8%，報每盎司 3346.60 美元。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>現貨價下跌 1.1%，報每盎司 3316.13 美元。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>本周仍上漲 0.8％。</li>\n</ul></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國勞工部周五公布，5 月非農就業人口新增 13.9 萬人，優於市場預估的 13 萬人，失業率持平在 4.2%，符合市場預期。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Marex 分析師 Edward Meir 說，非農數據顯示，Fed 可能會再按兵不動一段時間，這對<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>來說不利。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據短期利率合約，Fed 可能等到 9 月才會恢復降息，而且 12 月之前只會再降一次，對第三次降息的押注則降低了。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>是面對政治和經濟不確定性的避險資產，但高利率會降低<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>的魅力，因為<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>本身不孳息。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另一方面，即使美國總統川普和中國國家主席習近平周四通了電話，貿易政策方面的局勢依然不明朗。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Meir 說：「這些都是很艱難的協商，不會單靠通電話就能解決。如果關稅消息變成負面新聞，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>將看漲。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><h6>其他貴金屬交易</h6></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul>\n<li>現貨<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>下跌 0.5%，報每盎司 35.96 美元，稍早曾觸及超過 13 年以來的高點。</li>\n<li>現貨<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XPDUSDOZ\">白金</a>上漲 2.5%，報每盎司 1158.20 美元，是 2022 年 3 月以來最高。</li>\n<li>現貨<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XPTUSDOZ\">鈀金</a>上漲 3.9%，報每盎司 1045.45 美元。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XPDUSDOZ\">白金</a>和<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XPTUSDOZ\">鈀金</a>本周周線都上漲。</li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>瑞銀 (UBS) 分析師 Giovanni Staunovo 表示，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>的上漲「似乎是由投機資金所驅動，認為<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>相對於<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>太過便宜了，在<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>突破每盎司 35 美元關卡更放大了<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>的走勢。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
